## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="dd93e-158">下列程式碼範例會重設的幾何轉換的`pgBrush`身分識別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dd93e-158">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dd93e-159">假設`myPath`現有<xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dd93e-159">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
